# Task T-009@20260427T001208Z: Implement async worker loop `GenerationQueue.run_worker()` that processes pending items end-to-end.

## Acceptance Criteria

- `run_worker()` is an `async def` infinite loop<br/>- Each iteration: pull next `pending` (oldest first), check cache, check budget, generate, validate, store, mark `done` (or appropriate failure state)<br/>- Cache hit → mark done with `source="cache"` without paying<br/>- Budget deny → mark `blocked` (next iteration tries again with fresh budget after rollover)<br/>- `client.generate()` runs in `asyncio.to_thread` so the event loop stays responsive<br/>- `max_concurrent` limits parallel workers (default 1)<br/>- Tests with FakeClient verify each branch (cache hit, budget block, gen success, gen failure, validation reject)

